{"body": "> An observer implements :after_save to detect some state change. If detected, it wants to send a custom notification :some_state_changed, so other observers can be notified and don't have to reimplement the state change logic. It shouldn't have to use send.\r\n\r\nOn observer should only observe. It should not notify other observers. Observers are own way event consumption.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5424827", "created_at": "2012-04-30T18:57:07Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6093#issuecomment-5424827", "updated_at": "2012-04-30T18:57:07Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6093, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahawkins/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahawkins/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahawkins/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahawkins", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahawkins/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/ahawkins", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahawkins/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/464e254ea0f3d6af3958aa0259719a7c?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F58aebd719336ce690932d83d0f0162d5.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahawkins/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahawkins/received_events", "gravatar_id": "464e254ea0f3d6af3958aa0259719a7c", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahawkins/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "ahawkins", "type": "User", "id": 48928, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahawkins/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523e8459bd354364b901093b"}, "id": 5424827, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6093"}
